nt":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/bbRusTP8P9hX1D1Qdp4New3jjQu.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/uNT6RDgcFlvmtzXBkUPmU8JB1lG.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/n58jOGnMwf3x3ktBzjFfkiyCtzE.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/9wWGxnVqjxzW1pC2l1brQZEGsV0.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/nezyarrgKEEtdJlKfeoGNAvlM8Q.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/cg1p6rvICfuRc58zLOUYA87CWmf.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/5sKRoTh99Evt8wVmKHzGyDSHCcX.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/rDuf8QOLZiZxDA2yO4dzFErxXnc.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/yrRugvRSlou1IBxodPePd9T3vkg.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/ybqnVS9I7if9GfyBr01boBuz9uD.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2560,"height":1440,"file_path":"/hv5dMHhHBtp8l0q6y4phllQoPT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/dNQ7amISmis9q2IkzMsUBwYSev3.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-02-25T03:57:13.574+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Sidewalls","runtime":94,"tagline":"How do you find love when you don’t know where it is?","homepage":"http://www.medianeras.com/","overview":"Martin is a neurotic web designer taking baby steps out of the isolation of his one-room apartment and his virtual reality. Mariana is an artist fresh out of a a long relationship. They are perfect for each other, live on the same street, in opposite buildings, but they never meet. Can the movement of a modern city of three million people bring them together?"},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Medianeras","runtime":95,"tagline":"¿Cómo encontrar el amor si no sabés dónde está?","homepage":"http://www.medianeras.com/","overview":"Martín es un fóbico en vías de recuperación. De a poco va saliendo del encierro en su monoambiente y su adicción al mundo virtual. Mariana, recién separada, tiene tan desordenada la cabeza como el departamento en el que se refugia. ¿Deberían conocerse, no? ¿Cómo se pueden encontrar en una ciudad superpoblada y caótica como Buenos Aires? Medianeras. Lo mismo que los separa es lo que los une."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Medianeras - Buenos Aires da Era do Amor Virtual","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mariana (Pilar López de Ayala), Martin (Javier Drolas) e a cidade. Os dois vivem na mesma quadra, em apartamentos um de frente para o outro, mas nunca conseguem se encontrar. Eles se cruzam sem saber da existência do outro. Ela sobe as escadas, ele desce as escadas; ela entra no ônibus, ele sai do ônibus. Eles frequentam a mesma videolocadora, sempre com um stand de filmes os separando. Eles sentam na mesma fileira em um cinema, mas a sala é escura. A cidade que os coloca juntos é a mesma que os separa."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Yan Pencere","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Martin, günlerini dairesinde web tasarımı yapmakla geçiren bir agorafobiktir. Tedavi sürecinde, yavaş yavaş şehirde küçük turlar atmaya başlar. Mariana ise uzun bir ilişkinin post travmasını yaşamaktadır.  Karşılıklı dairelerde oturan bu yalnız erkek ve kadının karşılaşmalarını çaresizce bekleriz. Buenos Aires gibi üç milyon nüfuslu bir şehrin kaosunda ise bu pek de kolay olmaz.  Modern bir kent masalı anlatan film, büyük şehirlerdeki kent yaşamının nasıl kurgulandığını da mizahi ve ironik bir dille kurmaya çalışıyor. Kolektif bir nevrozdan muzdarip, yalnız bir adam ve kadının portresini çizerken; kaotik ve kalabalık Buenos Aires’in portresi de adım adım beliriyor zihnimizde."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Martin est phobique mais se soigne. Petit à petit il parvient à sortir de son isolement, de son studio et de sa réalité virtuelle. Il est web-designer. Mariana sort d'une relation longue. Elle est perdue et confuse, à l'image du désordre qui règne dans son appartement. Martin et Mariana vivent dans la même rue, dans des immeubles l'un en face de l'autre mais ne se sont jamais rencontrés. Ils fréquentent les mêmes endroits mais ne se remarquent pas. Comment peuvent-ils se rencontrer dans une ville de trois millions d'habitants? Ce qui les sépare les rassemble..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Medianeras - Innamorarsi a Buenos Aires","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Martin è un web designer. Internet gli ha cambiato la vita, nel senso che gliel'ha tolta completamente, poiché il ragazzo resta davanti al computer 24 ore al giorno: crea i suoi siti, gioca ai videogames, ordina il cibo, fcompra oggetti per la casa. Esce di rado, ma scoppia dal desiderio di vivere davvero. Peccato che, ogni volta che ci prova, finisca per tornare indietro e rinchiudersi nel suo claustrofobico monolocale. Mariana è un architetto. Potenzialmente, perché non hai mai veramente progettato neanche un bagno. Si guadagna da vivere allestendo vetrine, finendo per sentirsi fredda e vuota come i manichini che veste."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"קירות צדדיים","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"מרטין, מעצב אתרים שחי בבואנוס איירס, מנסה לצאת מהבדידות בה הוא חי ומהמציאות הוירטואלית לה התרגל. מריאנה סיימה לאחרונה מערכת יחסים והיא שבר כלי כמו הדירה בה מצאה מקלט. שניהם מתגוררים באותו רחוב, אחד מול השני, אבל מעולם לא נפגשו. איך הם יוכלו לפגוש אחת בשני בעיר בה שלושה מיליון תושבים?"},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"在人海中遇见你","runtime":94,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"他是一个只愿宅在家里的网站设计师，她是一个做着橱窗设计的建筑师。在这个信息科技高速发达的年代，无论是他还是她都在经受不同程度的精神压抑。他们住在同一个城市同一条街道，但是却像两条平行的直线从未有过交点。他们分别和各自的伴侣约会、分手，各自在寻找着那个正确的人。她是玛丽安娜（碧拉尔·洛佩兹·德·阿亚拉 Pilar López de Ayala 饰），他是马丁（哈维尔·多罗拉斯 Javier Drolas 饰），他们是布宜诺斯艾利斯里两个普通人。可是因为内心的执着，让玛丽安娜从未放弃由一本儿时图画书引发的追寻。也所幸那些“不正确的人”的离开，终于让冥冥注定的相遇终于实现。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Medianeras: Buenos Aires da Era do Amor Virtual","runtime":94,"tagline":"Como Encontrar o Amor se Você não Sabe Onde Ele Está?","homepage":"","overview":"Martin e Mariana vivem na mesma rua, em edifícios opostos, mas eles nunca se conheceram. Eles andam pelos mesmos lugares mas nunca notaram um ao outro. Quais são as chances deles se conhecerem em uma cidade de três milhões de habitantes? O que os separa, irá uni-los."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Martin en Mariana wonen en leven in Buenos Aires. In zekere zin zijn ze zelfs buren, want vanuit hun appartementen kunnen ze de flat van de ander zien. Soms passeren ze elkaar, maar ze zijn zich nooit van de ander bewust. Allebei zijn ze zoekende in het leven. Ze bezoeken dezelfde videotheek, maar worden gescheiden door een rek met films. Ze zitten zelfs vlak bij elkaar in de bioscoopzaal, maar het is te donker om elkaar te kunnen herkennen. Het is de stad die Martin en Mariana samenbrengt, maar die hen ook van elkaar gescheiden houdt."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"부에노스 아이레스에서 사랑에 빠질 확률","runtime":0,"tagline":"수 많은 사람들 가운데, 우리는 끝내 만나게 될 거에요! 매칭률 100%를 향한 도시남녀의 신개념 러브스토리!","homepage":"","overview":"산타 페 1105번지4층, H호\r 외부와의 접촉을 최소화한 채 컴퓨터로 모든 생활을 해결하는 웹 디자이너 마틴.\r 오늘도 그의 곁을 지키는 건 7년 전 헤어진 여자친구의 강아지 수수 뿐이다.\r 마틴에게 온라인 채팅은 일상처럼 익숙하지만, 낯선 이와의 데이트는 어색하고 불편하기만 하다.  산타 페 1183번지8층, G호\r 도시의 쇼윈도를 디자인하는 디스플레이어 마리아나.\r 힘겨웠던 4년 간의 연애를 끝내고 집에 돌아왔지만 그녀를 반기는 건 묵묵부답의 마네킹 뿐이다.\r 이별 후의 밤이 유독 힘겨운 마리아나는 오늘도 이 도시 어딘가에 있을 운명의 상대를 상상한다.  갑작스런 정전으로 모든 게 멈춰버린 밤, 집 밖으로 나선 마틴과 마리아나.\r 가까이 있으면서도 서로의 존재를 모르던 그들은 과연 사랑을 이룰 수 있을까?"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Глухие стены","runtime":95,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Марианна и Мартин — люди, страдающие душевно и пытающиеся вернуться к нормальной жизни. Они живут на одной и той же улице, в домах, стоящих друг напротив друга, но никогда не встречались. Он — веб-дизайнер. Она переживает расставание после длительных отношений. Они идут по тем же самым улицам и не замечают друг друга. Разве они не должны встретиться? Однако как это сделать в таком переполненном, хаотичном городе, как Буэнос-Айрес?"},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Identita velkých měst spočívá v jejich budovách. Dnes je to často chaotická směs různorodých a neslučitelných architektonických stylů. Kontemplací o Buenos Aires přechází snímek zároveň k pozorování jeho stejně nesourodých obyvatel: Martín je allenovsky neurotický intelektuál, „ajťák“, kterému internet přiblížil svět, ale zároveň ho vzdálil životu. Přítelkyně mu utekla do Ameriky a nechala mu psa. Je typickým obyvatelem metropole stejně jako Mariana. Oba žijí ve stejné čtvrti, ulici, bloku..."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Μεσοτοιχίες","runtime":0,"tagline":"Πως να βρείς τον έρωτα όταν δεν ξέρεις που να ψάξεις;","homepage":"","overview":"Η Mariana και ο Martin ζουν στο ίδιο οικοδομικό τετράγωνο του Μπουένος Άιρες. Καθημερινά οι δρόμοι τους διασταυρώνονται. Ψωνίζουν στα ίδια μαγαζιά, κολυμπούν στην ίδια πισίνα αλλά δεν έχουν γνωριστεί ποτέ. Ο Martin βγαίνει σπάνια από το σπίτι μετά τον χωρισμό του. Περνά τις μέρες παρέα με το σκυλάκι που του άφησε η προηγούμενη κοπέλα του όταν έφυγε για την Αμερική. Η Mariana είναι αρχιτέκτονας αλλά μέχρι να σχεδιάσει κάποιο κτήριο διακοσμεί βιτρίνες σε καταστήματα ρούχων. Έχει μόλις βγει από μια τετράχρονη σχέση που την τσάκισε ψυχολογικά και δεν αισθάνεται ικανή να κάνει μια καινούργια αρχή."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"ブエノスアイレス恋愛事情","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Mitgeres","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"在人海中遇見你","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"他是一個只願宅在家裏的網站設計師，她是一個做著櫥窗設計的建築師。在這個信息科技高速發達的年代，無論是他還是她都在經受不同程度的精神壓抑。他們住在同一個城市同一條街道，但是卻像兩條平行的直線從未有過交點。他們分別和各自的伴侶約會、分手，各自在尋找著那個正確的人。她是瑪麗安娜（碧拉爾·洛佩茲·德·阿亞拉 Pilar López de Ayala 飾），他是馬丁（哈維爾·多羅拉斯 Javier Drolas 飾），他們是布宜諾斯艾利斯裏兩個普通人。可是因為內心的執著，讓瑪麗安娜從未放棄由一本兒時圖畫書引發的追尋。也所幸那些“不正確的人”的離開，終於讓冥冥註定的相遇終於實現。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"6355d4dea06efe007f28b217","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/6355d4dea06efe007f28b217","author":"badelf","content":"In the category of romantic comedies, this film is creative and funny. And it is sooooooo adorable!","created_at":"2022-10-23T23:57:18.613Z","updated_at":"2022-10-23T23:57:18.688Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"badelf","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":328301,"adult":false,"title":"Sidewalls","video":false,"overview":"Mariana and Martin have similar lives: the same loneliness, the same neurosis, even the same apartment, but they can’t meet. Their only link is also what separates them: the sidewall.","genre_ids":[10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.413,"vote_count":15,"poster_path":"/hSi1tnK9S4jYxiLRs7R5SCk0GkZ.jpg","release_date":"2006-05-14","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/h4G01Ycu218S54YED1uUUG63rCD.jpg","original_title":"Medianeras","original_language":"es"},{"id":846716,"adult":false,"title":"The Hand","video":false,"overview":"Hong Kong, 1960s. Zhang, a shy tailor's assistant, is riveted by his imperious client Miss Hua. Upon meeting her, she seduces him to make sure he will truly remember her when designing her garments. After this intimate first encounter, a rapport develops between the two. Entry is for the theatrically released extended version, not the segment from the Eros anthology.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7246,"vote_count":37,"poster_path":"/nZ9BfIiEktWis3D05BNYx9YqVL3.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-03","vote_average":7.095,"backdrop_path":"/r4pDYHM7BQto4UEDmypytQ7IvSa.jpg","original_title":"手","original_language":"zh"},{"id":51378,"adult":false,"title":"Intimate Stories","video":false,"overview":"Three people and a baby set off on separate journeys, along the same road; their disparate dreams and stories intertwine amidst the breathtaking deserted Patagonic route.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3237,"vote_count":63,"poster_path":"/dD27iIMNImAnGlSs7OroS0lvV95.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-24","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/w2QUsItk4yAo0UwW86QJxnxgs5F.jpg","original_title":"Historias mínimas","original_language":"es"},{"id":362876,"adult":false,"title":"California","video":false,"overview":"The year is 1984. Estela is going through the turbulent phase of adolescence. Sex, lovers, friendships; everything seems very complicated. Her uncle Carlos is her hero, and visiting him in California is her biggest dream. But everything collapses when he returns thin, weak and ill. Between crises and discoveries, Estela will face a reality that will forever change her way of seeing the world.​","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4696,"vote_count":48,"poster_path":"/nTonUzjWK6mhXYYrf5xsmSGccrS.jpg","release_date":"2015-12-03","vote_average":7.135,"backdrop_path":"/qjQ4oTfXuHtzq6u3FczF8p4Lrre.jpg","original_title":"Califórnia","original_language":"pt"},{"id":42164,"adult":false,"title":"Camera Buff","video":false,"overview":"Filip buys an 8mm movie camera when his first child is born. Because it's the first camera in town, he's named official photographer by the local Party boss. His horizons widen when he is sent to regional film festivals with his first works but his focus on movie making also leads to domestic strife and philosophical dilemmas.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5552,"vote_count":183,"poster_path":"/l4n9LXUanIKdlKTCfRqrhwQbtVe.jpg","release_date":"1979-11-16","vote_average":7.492,"backdrop_path":"/zMzh7y3bcvFdHxPFedOOp8zFgOS.jpg","original_title":"Amator","original_language":"pl"},{"id":157115,"adult":false,"title":"Jug Face","video":false,"overview":"When a supernatural pit worshipped by a remote community in the woods demands a new blood sacrifice, a young woman struggles to find a way to survive as the pit lashes out in anger.","genre_ids":[27,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6764,"vote_count":189,"poster_path":"/tBNRzn69tdvQPiKNNu5RA3WcMx9.jpg","release_date":"2013-08-09","vote_average":5.251,"backdrop_path":"/6wk73hNnSHqvIbxWHFb9WLRgvNn.jpg","original_title":"Jug Face","original_language":"en"},{"id":27605,"adult":false,"title":"The 13 Roses","video":false,"overview":"True story of thirteen totally normal young women that suffered harsh questioning and were put in prison under made up charges of helping the rebellion against Franco back in the 1940s. Despite of their innocence, the thirteen were soon executed without even a trace of evidence of any wrong doing.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5216,"vote_count":93,"poster_path":"/nsU48KgwfXuygvY92plG5NSqalw.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-19","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/263koDAEckD9nZFw4ESBUht5gz3.jpg","original_title":"Las 13 rosas","original_language":"es"},{"id":331354,"adult":false,"title":"Requirements to Be a Normal Person","video":false,"overview":"Maria is 30 years old, she is a peculiar person and has one goal: become a normal person. But first of all she must discover what is exactly this. Which kind of person is she? Is she a normal person? What does exactly means? That question goes deeper into her mind. After she lists every requirements, she proposes to reach them. In that journey she will find her brother's help, Alex, a 25 years old boy who is mentally challenged and achieves every list requirements. She meets Borja as well, a boy obsessed with diets and lose weight. They will make a curious pact: she helps him to live an active and healthy live, and he helps her to meet her goal: become a normal person.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.249,"vote_count":134,"poster_path":"/vujRsKU37cPAyRlILCZNgOXuKxk.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-04","vote_average":6.396,"backdrop_path":"/nm9xMYSK9LtZLLLSisyb0QpBMHX.jpg","original_title":"Requisitos para ser una persona normal","original_language":"es"},{"id":57276,"adult":false,"title":"Pina","video":false,"overview":"Pina is a feature-length dance film in 3D with the ensemble of the Tanztheater Wuppertal Pina Bausch, featuring the unique and inspiring art of the great German choreographer, who died in the summer of 2009.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.579,"vote_count":271,"poster_path":"/mKKtIJYtaGwcgpMfnVR2byYhfz9.jpg","release_date":"2011-02-24","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/p6GI3J6CfxhxwYmvHpBtYRVi7iq.jpg","original_title":"Pina","original_language":"de"},{"id":127,"adult":false,"title":"Blind Chance","video":false,"overview":"Witek runs after a train. Three variations follow on how such a seemingly banal incident could influence the rest of Witek's life.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6128,"vote_count":234,"poster_path":"/gx84VmJllqvXF3JEqcEdsxBEcbF.jpg","release_date":"1987-01-10","vote_average":7.545,"backdrop_path":"/eTSRN1Bwce60rpAORwkKbPRDT6V.jpg","original_title":"Przypadek","original_language":"pl"},{"id":11477,"adult":false,"title":"Common Wealth","video":false,"overview":"After finding an enormous amount of money hidden in a dead man's apartment, real estate agent Julia must face the wrath of the very peculiar inhabitants of the apartment building, who will stop at nothing to get their hands on the money.","genre_ids":[35,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5902,"vote_count":339,"poster_path":"/witJ36VoxVAu62lpcyBhiKtAMAn.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-29","vote_average":6.912,"backdrop_path":"/lTjyjtr1NLNfeglWKzLS3gPW94v.jpg","original_title":"La comunidad","original_language":"es"},{"id":53961,"adult":false,"title":"Brainstorm","video":false,"overview":"Neto is a middle class teenager living a normal life. After his father finds a marijuana cigarette on his pocket, he is sent to a mental institution, where he gets to know a completely absurd and inhumane reality in which people are devoured by a corrupt and cruel system.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5194,"vote_count":225,"poster_path":"/x6NXI2jvi9iKbzjjHRMtZ7mCPjB.jpg","release_date":"2001-06-22","vote_average":7.9,"backdrop_path":"/nwPHdJp7bwFCFwcxUTuqHvtcESi.jpg","original_title":"Bicho de Sete Cabeças","original_language":"pt"},{"id":118662,"adult":false,"title":"Decalogue I","video":false,"overview":"Krzysztof, a semantics professor and computer hobbyist, is raising his young son, Paweł, to look to science for answers, while Irena, Paweł’s aunt, lives a life rooted in faith. Over the course of one day, both adults are forced to question their belief systems.","genre_ids":[18,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3903,"vote_count":257,"poster_path":"/h3kJ2UXkZSUzfQAAjcRwl6qNIpc.jpg","release_date":"1989-05-16","vote_average":8.101,"backdrop_path":"/aldfhBj8nq2GLYr8qozR1u0G2NY.jpg","original_title":"Dekalog, jeden","original_language":"pl"},{"id":13537,"adult":false,"title":"Shattered Glass","video":false,"overview":"The true story of fraudulent Washington, D.C. journalist Stephen Glass, who rose to meteoric heights as a young writer in his 20s, becoming a staff writer at The New Republic for three years. Looking for a short cut to fame, Glass concocted sources, quotes and even entire stories, but his deception did not go unnoticed forever, and eventually, his world came crumbling down.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.967,"vote_count":461,"poster_path":"/1KHHNkrf8t15sXXF9d9TGq1T9jv.jpg","release_date":"2003-11-14","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/u4OUSKeFwuP1z42dL58Mi0LYwIg.jpg","original_title":"Shattered Glass","original_language":"en"},{"id":575428,"adult":false,"title":"The Wild Goose Lake","video":false,"overview":"A gangster ends up making a mistake that causes every gun on both sides of the law to point at him. While on the run, he comes across a mysterious woman who might get him out of trouble or make things worse.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0895,"vote_count":364,"poster_path":"/w49o4vmNFpCt4VFJp7ip6tjHh3x.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-06","vote_average":6.659,"backdrop_path":"/h9xzx7FteH3kFcED51qYjeHHUHD.jpg","original_title":"南方车站的聚会","original_language":"zh"},{"id":67884,"adult":false,"title":"Chinese Take-Away","video":false,"overview":"A comedy that chronicles a chance encounter between Robert and a Chinese named Jun who wanders lost through the city of Buenos Aires in search of his uncle after being assaulted by a taxi driver and his henchmen.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.631,"vote_count":429,"poster_path":"/wSrMT1YrcMH4NdzH7IdJaQzgzJc.jpg","release_date":"2011-03-24","vote_average":7.239,"backdrop_path":"/fqRJLbbakXAT88XTBVz0no4xavg.jpg","original_title":"Un cuento chino","original_language":"es"},{"id":72478,"adult":false,"title":"Suicide Room","video":false,"overview":"Moody, dark and handsome Dominik is terrorized at school after video footage of his drunken kiss with classmate Aleksandr goes viral. Grappling with public humiliation, Dominik seeks solace in an avatar based 'suicide room' where the pink-haired rebel Sylwia consoles him.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6234,"vote_count":474,"poster_path":"/6BUyvSeRG4FAkv0jo5FhJ87gHMw.jpg","release_date":"2011-03-04","vote_average":7.283,"backdrop_path":"/zGNLkZYzFrBvROL2g6UNJsfnA8h.jpg","original_title":"Sala samobójców","original_language":"pl"},{"id":17483,"adult":false,"title":"Shelter","video":false,"overview":"Forced to give up his dreams of art school, Zach works dead-end jobs to support his sister and her son. Questioning his life, he paints, surfs and hangs out with his best friend, Gabe. When Gabe's older brother returns home for the summer, Zach suddenly finds himself drawn into a relationship he didn't expect.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.3776,"vote_count":497,"poster_path":"/eYA8KiSnIAbxtoIgg4lpZjB0dfz.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-16","vote_average":7.755,"backdrop_path":"/4cK3YaPMAnyfqrpfMXlB9qyQbAL.jpg","original_title":"Shelter","original_language":"en"},{"id":332872,"adult":false,"title":"Julieta","video":false,"overview":"The film spans 30 years in Julieta’s life from a nostalgic 1985 where everything seems hopeful, to 2015 where her life appears to be beyond repair and she is on the verge of madness.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2812,"vote_count":906,"poster_path":"/z4aErD1RQQ3alpu3PoUu408HEVc.jpg","release_date":"2016-04-08","vote_average":6.986,"backdrop_path":"/yG8iQi4gX0tjUBAvMNsliES3Czy.jpg","original_title":"Julieta","original_language":"es"},{"id":96936,"adult":false,"title":"The Bling Ring","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by actual events, a group of fame-obsessed teenagers use the Internet to track celebrities' whereabouts in order to rob their homes.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5182,"vote_count":3119,"poster_path":"/6yh55qCcdgPRJweDWM2CiEubJCL.jpg","release_date":"2013-06-12","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/ouN0GyE7mtIT6wyJeilaggyvgNj.jpg","original_title":"The Bling Ring","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":48414,"adult":false,"title":"To the Sea","video":false,"overview":"Before leaving for Rome with his mother, five year old Natan  is taken by his father, Jorge, on an epic journey to the pristine Chinchorro reef off the coast of Mexico. As they fish, swim, and sail the turquoise waters of the open sea, Natan discovers the beauty of his Mayan heritage and learns to live in harmony with life above and below the surface, as the bond between father and son grows stronger before their inevitable farewell.","genre_ids":[99,10751,18],"popularity":2.2326,"vote_count":50,"poster_path":"/kakeJZOFUONyDFTLaSxfFJuAib1.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-01","vote_average":6.89,"backdrop_path":"/yg4DNTCX1Z8onZxNOAyX95gJB5c.jpg","original_title":"Alamar","original_language":"es"},{"id":1298368,"adult":false,"title":"Momo","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1329,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/mYLAURg9xh1zAWxInzlNc73Lzyl.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-23","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Momo","original_language":"nl"},{"id":49574,"adult":false,"title":"Cloud Heaven","video":false,"overview":"In this gentle comedy, an unpopular resident in a Russian village has his life completely changed when he announces, entirely on a whim and just to upset things a bit, that he's moving to the Pacific coast.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.1877,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/g3KrNS9KtPxtc3uj9lsOnqjDwje.jpg","release_date":"1990-12-04","vote_average":6.426,"backdrop_path":"/ahqLZlIBTVgp0w2RtzejSGMj4wu.jpg","original_title":"Облако-рай","original_language":"ru"},{"id":298945,"adult":false,"title":"Evadi Gola Vadide","video":false,"overview":"Veera loves Aarti but his marriage is fixed to the daughter of powerful don Bakka Reddy. When Bakka learns about Veera's intentions, he orders his men to kill Aarti.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"popularity":0.1935,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/dxXgXm4YvSgPmIgQhvhYgpjJq6m.jpg","release_date":"2005-01-21","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"ఎవడి గోల వాడిది","original_language":"te"},{"id":308369,"adult":false,"title":"Me and Earl and the Dying Girl","video":false,"overview":"Greg is coasting through senior year of high school as anonymously as possible, avoiding social interactions like the plague while secretly making spirited, bizarre films with Earl, his only friend. But both his anonymity and friendship threaten to unravel when his mother forces him to befriend a classmate with leukemia.","genre_ids":[18,35],"popularity":1.7434,"vote_count":2709,"poster_path":"/eLjS2bLMjln2n2I73Xu6TaANPDZ.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-12","vote_average":7.531,"backdrop_path":"/4sOeeDX9uBteu81ty2bcdbzU933.jpg","original_title":"Me and Earl and the Dying Girl","original_language":"en"},{"id":896151,"adult":false,"title":"Blitz","video":false,"overview":"In World War II London, nine-year-old George is evacuated to the countryside by his mother, Rita, to escape the bombings. Defiant and determined to return to his family, George embarks on an epic, perilous journey back home as Rita searches for him.","genre_ids":[10752,18,36],"popularity":1.7172,"vote_count":236,"poster_path":"/e9tyjbF2rugENtBolTtEhHOXgzD.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-01","vote_average":5.998,"backdrop_path":"/qRSMoh9EMlQ9uywMpLulWBkIma9.jpg","original_title":"Blitz","original_language":"en"},{"id":520372,"adult":false,"title":"Paradise Lost?","video":false,"overview":"After discovering that John Milton is buried within London's Barbican grounds, Iain Forsyth & Jane Pollard reimagined his epic poem ‘Paradise Lost’ as part of Doug Aitken's Station to Station project. The piece uses the architecture and atmosphere of the Barbican to update the story, which is told in three parts.","genre_ids":[18,14,53],"popularity":0.2441,"vote_count":11,"poster_path":"/48gGrHER7Z26VjGexGCGOyoVM30.jpg","release_date":"2015-07-26","vote_average":6.091,"backdrop_path":"/l9443X9enlw7hUJNubddcipd3Y1.jpg","original_title":"Paradise Lost?","original_language":"en"},{"id":520172,"adult":false,"title":"Happiest Season","video":false,"overview":"A young woman's plans to propose to her girlfriend while at her family's annual holiday party are upended when she discovers her partner hasn't yet come out to her conservative parents.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"popularity":2.0214,"vote_count":1306,"poster_path":"/vzec9kkOSE93tygyfOktedkeOQ.jpg","release_date":"2020-11-26","vote_average":7.099,"backdrop_path":"/jOWgFmD1H5t6nL7ChbmX8oDFUZl.jpg","original_title":"Happiest Season","original_language":"en"},{"id":713776,"adult":false,"title":"If Anything Happens I Love You","video":false,"overview":"In this Oscar-winning short film, grieving parents journey through an emotional void as they mourn the loss of a child after a tragic school shooting.","genre_ids":[18,16],"popularity":0.6332,"vote_count":970,"poster_path":"/85tDhACvKDQxQoJhBYLvDU