Val spends the next 13 years working as a nanny to Fabinho in São Paulo. She has financial stability but has to live with the guilt of having not raised Jessica herself. As Fabinho’s university entrance exams approach, Jessica reappears in her life and seems to want to give her mother a second chance. However, Jessica has not been raised to be a servant and her very existence will turn Val’s routine on its head. With precision and humour, the subtle and powerful forces that keep rigid class structures in place and how the youth may just be the ones to shake it all up.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.9203,"vote_count":769,"poster_path":"/u1tDQun2iJAzersd94S8P47WEOL.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-04","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/9h5BsxRmxLAvASADo2VcTlTUdb0.jpg","original_title":"Que Horas Ela Volta?","original_language":"pt"},{"id":308084,"adult":false,"title":"Tangerine","video":false,"overview":"It's Christmas Eve in Tinseltown and Sin-Dee is back on the block. Upon hearing that her pimp boyfriend hasn't been faithful during the 28 days she was locked up, the working girl and her best friend, Alexandra, embark on a mission to get to the bottom of the scandalous rumor. Their rip-roaring odyssey leads them through various subcultures of Los Angeles, including an Armenian family dealing with their own repercussions of infidelity.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":4.5587,"vote_count":781,"poster_path":"/EKLR5c61XQzBTeMokFrmS3kdt8.jpg","release_date":"2015-07-10","vote_average":6.876,"backdrop_path":"/q18pdMKGX4wSHaT3lllt5jLjp8d.jpg","original_title":"Tangerine","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt1235841","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":"MedianerasTheFilm","wikidata_id":"Q3428553","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/sidewalls","mydramalist_id":"204336","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/sidewalls_2011"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":"MedianerasTheFilm","instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148397,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_g